                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Eustis</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 6, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Waller’s wife and children, having left Madagascar, are reported destitute in
                    Mauritius. Consul at Port Louis has been telegraphed to draw on you for
                    reasonable expense of sending them to Paris, whence you will send them home.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
